5
00:00:22,790 --> 00:00:25,390
Choi Yeon Woo, you're also a Mono?

6
00:00:26,830 --> 00:00:28,470
Yes.

7
00:00:28,470 --> 00:00:30,570
...also?

8
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:34,640
