15
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:06,470
What do you all think?

16
00:01:06,470 --> 00:01:08,510
Probe surgery?

17
00:01:10,450 --> 00:01:12,570
They said it was due to infection.

18
00:01:12,570 --> 00:01:16,630
