23
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:38,080
A surgery that stimulates Mono to recognize colors. That's Probe surgery.

24
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:42,200
But I can't believe such surgery exists.

25
00:01:45,730 --> 00:01:47,750
Ye Won didn't have a Probe,

26
00:01:47,750 --> 00:01:51,690
so she was very envious of Yi Ri since she met hers.

27
00:01:51,690 --> 00:01:56,970
I believe she said it was the love of a century or something.

28
00:01:56,970 --> 00:01:58,660
I see...

29
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:05,530
She went through a lot of hardship at such a young age because she suddenly became the administrator.

30
00:02:05,530 --> 00:02:07,020
Administrator?

31
